{"lemma":"شَمَط","slug":"شَمَط","root":"ش.م.ط","root_slug":"ش-م-ط","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-م-ط","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23013","","n23014"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B7"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23013","headword_ar":"شَمِطَ","root":"$mT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaTN","text_ar":"شَمَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, grizzled in the hair of his head; he had whiteness in the hair of his head, mixed with its blackness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, * K:) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$omaTa","text_ar":"اَشْمَطَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, but wanting in one copy,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$omaT~a","text_ar":"اِشْمَطَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$omaAT~a","text_ar":"اِشْمَاطَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$omaA^aT~a","text_ar":"اِشْمَاَطَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had hair of two different colours, black and white:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had whiteness of the hair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoariness, mixed with the blackness of youth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had whiteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoariness, in his beard:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amiTato","text_ar":"شَمِطَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a woman,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she had whiteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoariness, in the head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaTN","text_ar":"شَمَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaTa","text_ar":"شَمَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amoTN","text_ar":"شَمْطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing; (S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he mixed together"},{"kind":"text","text":"any two things: (S, Mgh:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$omaTa","text_ar":"اَشْمَطَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (AZ, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayaTa bayona AlmaA='i waAll~abani","text_ar":"شَيَطَ بَيْنَ المَا=ءِ وَاللَّبَنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He mixed together the water and the milk."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamalaka biSadaqapK","text_ar":"عَمَلَكَ بِصَدَقَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$omiTo","text_ar":"اَشْمِطْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mix thou thy work with alms."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ.) And Aboo-'Amr Ibn-El-'Alà used to say to his companions,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$omiTuwA","text_ar":"اشْمِطُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", [i. e. either"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1598},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ai$omiTuwA","text_ar":"اِشْمِطُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$omiTuwA","text_ar":"اَشْمِطُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",] meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Betake yourselves at one time to reading,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reciting, somewhat of the Kur-án, and another time to some tradition, and another time to something strange"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is to be elucidated"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and another time to poetry, and another time to lexicology;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mix ye these"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subjects of study"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or, accord. to one relation, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$am~iTuwA","text_ar":"شَمِّطُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Har p. 177; where it is expl. in a similar manner)."}],"source_refs":["K","S","Mgh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n23014","headword_ar":"شَمَطٌ","root":"$mT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whiteness of the hair of the head mixed with its blackness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difference"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the hair"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by being of two colours, black and white:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mixture of whiteness of the hair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoariness, with the blackness of youth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or in a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoariness, of the beard:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, Mgh, TA:) but in a woman,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoariness, of the head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA.) [See 1.] ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaTaAtN","text_ar":"شَمَطَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is its pl.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"White hairs that are in the head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","K","M","TA","Lth"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}